{
  "stem": "11641.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 88.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So nobody told me something about what happened to my family.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Prior to that, I forgot to tell you, my brother was arrested by the Jewish police in Bochnia ghetto, and he was accused of belonging to the Jewish underground.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that's the last I heard of him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I had in my mind to tell you this, but something happened.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that's the last I heard of him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, he was.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I didn't know, because he didn't want to tell me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because if he tell me, and they catch me, I would sort of spill the beans.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I just found out from somebody-- somebody else.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I knew that he was a [NON-ENGLISH], like an interrogation center in Krakow, and then he was sent to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So in the meantime, I knew that when they liquidated the ghetto that nobody was surviving.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I said to Abush, I said, Abush, we have to get out of here.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This doesn't-- doesn't work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So there was a big line over there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said, what's this line for?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They said, you know what?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This line is for a guy named Schindler-- Oskar Schindler.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I said, who is he?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He said, he needs some people to work for him outside the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I said, Abush, I don't care where he is.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "As long as we get out of here, we stay in line.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We stayed in line, standing with about 400 people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "How many people he needs?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He said, about 100.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I said, Abush, we're never going to make it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the meantime, the Jewish police, the camp Jewish police are minding order in line.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they're hitting here, hitting there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One guy called somebody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said, Steiner, just take care of this over here.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I heard the word, Steiner.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
